metadata.name: La Douceur des Fraises üçì
metadata.description:
Fraise is a young pastry chef living far from the city. She says that her mind feels more free to create there.
Each fruit used in her desserts comes from her own vegetable garden she cherishes with all her heart.
Her specialty is still strawberry desserts!

It is said that, by crossing her path, one would smell the sweet fragrance of strawberry...
